{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Figure 1 illustrates the PTQ-QLoRA integration.",
    "Our steps are as follows:",
    "We first employ full-parameter supervised fine-tuning (SFT) using a mixture of general instruction-following data and our internal tasks' training data on a pre-trained model, to obtain the fine-tuned model (in 16-bit).",
    "We then apply 4-bit Post-training Quantization (PTQ) on the 16-bit fine-tuned model, to obtain the quantized 4-bit model.",
    "Lastly, we leverage the QLoRA (Dettmers et al., 2023) approach to do another round of SFT on the quantized 4-bit model through a LoRA (Hu et al., 2022b)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Lastly, we leverage the QLoRA (Dettmers et al., 2023) approach to do another round of SFT on the quantized 4-bit model through a LoRA (Hu et al., 2022b)."
  ]
}